headline: Martin Marietta (MLM) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Lag Estimates
summary: Martin Marietta (MLM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -17.76% and -1.34%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
